  <h1>Privacy Policy – QuitScore</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> February 28, 2026</p>

  <section>
    <p>QuitScore (“we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information when you use our mobile application <strong>QuitScore</strong>.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Email address (if you create an account), Name or nickname (optional), Profile information you provide voluntarily.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Information:</strong> App activity and progress (e.g., days without smoking, life saved metrics), Device type, OS version, app version, Crash logs and performance data.</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> We may use third-party analytics services to understand how users interact with the app, improve features, and monitor performance.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To operate, maintain, and improve the app</li>
      <li>To provide personalized features and content</li>
      <li>To respond to support requests</li>
      <li>To send app updates, notifications, or promotional communications (if you opt-in)</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. How We Share Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share your information in the following circumstances:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>With service providers who perform services on our behalf (analytics, cloud storage, notifications)</li>
      <li>If required by law or legal process</li>
      <li>To protect rights, safety, or property</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Data is stored securely on cloud servers.</li>
      <li>We implement reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your data.</li>
      <li>No data transmission over the internet is 100% secure. Use the app at your own risk.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your location (e.g., under GDPR or CCPA), you may have rights to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal information</li>
      <li>Opt-out of certain data collection</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise your rights, contact us at: <a href="mailto:yuriiyudin@icloud.com">yuriiyudin@icloud.com</a></p>
  </section>

